Text length: 4461, reading time approximately 7.5 minutes

Introduction: February 19 is also the new week for Ying Yong and Wang Zhonglin. On This Day, the information on the micro-blog platform about the help-seeking of the new pneumonia patients was cleared to zero.

Author | Caijing No. 1 Xu Huiyun

Shortly after the opening of Beijing Xiaotangshan Hospital, SARS ushered in an inflection point. If we understand the meaning of Xiaotangshan in 2003, we can understand the "Wuhan version of Xiaotangshan" and Thor Mountain, carrying what kind of expectations.

Author | Caijing No. 1 Xu Huiyun

Shortly after the opening of Beijing Xiaotangshan Hospital, SARS ushered in an inflection point. If we understand the meaning of Xiaotangshan in 2003, we can understand the "Wuhan version of Xiaotangshan" and Thor Mountain, carrying what kind of expectations.

This is the beginning of Wuhan's attempt to reverse the "hard to get a bed" , hoping to change the passive situation from "people waiting for beds" to "beds waiting for people" initiative. But looking back, the process has not been easy.

Desperate Times call for desperate measures. In the epidemic prevention and control into the "most difficult key stage, " February 13, Wuhan, Hubei Province at the same time to replace the commander. In the past ten days or so, has Wuhan's war-epidemic fighting method changed? Is The execution in place? Has the situation changed?

"Bed's waiting. "

On January 28, there were 5,974 confirmed cases of new pneumonia in 31 provinces and municipalities in China, surpassing the 2003 SARS outbreak. Since then, the numbers have climbed rapidly, reminding people that Vulcan and thor are not the final answer.

On February 3 alone, 1,242 new cases were confirmed in Wuhan, more than the number of beds on Mount Vulcan.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
An ambulance transporting a confirmed patient arrived at Wuhan Huoshenshan Hospital on February 8.

Because the hospital does not have the bed, can not do the nucleic acid examination in time, the massive confirmed diagnosis, the suspected patient can not receive treatment, causes the result, one is becomes "the moving infectious source" , has the serious cross infection, especially the family gathers the sex infection; One is to speed up the evolution of the disease course, from mild to severe, resulting in Wuhan severe, critical cases of high proportion.

Ding Xiangyang, Deputy secretary-general of the State Council and a member of the central guidance team, said at a news conference in Wuhan on February 20 that the sudden outbreak was a "battle" in a very unusual battle since the founding ceremony of the People's Republic of China, the scale of the epidemic, the scale of its spread, and the scale of the challenges and pressures facing society as a whole are indeed unprecedented.

Regarding the situation after January 27, Ding Xiangyang said that judging from the newly reported cases, it should be said that the epidemic in Wuhan, Hubei Province has emerged as a pandemic, showing a point-like, localized outbreak and a large area of multiple sites with multiple outbreaks.

As of February 11,44,672 confirmed cases had been reported in mainland China, according to an epidemiological study by the COVID-19 of the Chinese Center for Disease Control and Prevention, 73.1% of the onset occurred in January. In particular, the first epidemic peak was reached from January 24 to 28, and the daily abnormal high of one-day incidence occurred on February 1.

As of the reporting date, the reported cases peaked on 5 February, almost 10 days later, after which they remained relatively high and slowly declined.

"There are a large number of patients in Wuhan, Hubei Province. The beds are seriously inadequate and the masses can not be admitted to the upper house. The pressure of the rescue work is very great, and we are burning with anxiety, " Ding Xiangyang said on the 20th.

The task of increasing beds is to point first to the hospital. Wuhan continued to increase the number of designated hospitals, while transforming the general ward into an isolation ward for the treatment of infectious patients. But "the speed of the renovation depends not only on the progress of construction, but also on the speed of medical supplies, such as first-aid equipment, which is matched by inhalation, " said a doctor at a designated hospital.

The continuous "tight balance" of medical materials has affected the promotion of "collecting and treating as much as possible" .

Another problem is that the turnover rate of hospital beds in Wuhan is very low.

On February 4, Jiao Yahui, deputy director of the medical and Health Administration Bureau of the National Health Commission, announced that the average length of stay for patients discharged from hospitals outside Hubei Province was more than nine days, while the average length of stay in Hubei Province was 20 days.

The shortage of beds, combined with low turnover rate, makes the existing hospital beds in Wuhan and the actual effectiveness of the discount. "should be collected, should be treated" in the existing hospital level, can not be resolved.

Large Space, multi-bed shelter hospital, is an important move to reverse the situation in Wuhan.

Wang Chen, vice president of the Chinese Academy of Engineering and President of the Chinese Academy of Medical Sciences, said in an interview with the media that it is crucial to quickly admit all patients diagnosed with mild illness to avoid causing new infections, the construction of "Shelter Hospital" is of great significance to the prevention and control of epidemic situation.

On the night of February 3, three "shelter hospitals" were built in Wuhan, including the Wembley Arena, the living room and the Wuhan International Convention and Exhibition Center. On the morning of the 4th, it was announced that three more "shelter hospitals" would be built in Guanggu Science and Technology Exhibition Center, Wuhan Sports Center Stadium Center and Wuhan International Expo Center.

At 10 pm on February 5, the Kong Hon Shelter Hospital at the Wuhan International Convention and Exhibition Center opened. Early on February 6, Ling Hong (not his real name) , a 48-year-old Wuhan resident, checked in. "It's a bit of a relief to move in. "

Ling Hong is a mild case, he basically does not have a fever, but feel hoarse difficulty, lack of energy. Quarantined at home since his diagnosis on February 3rd.

Although the beginning of admission encountered some inconvenience, but soon, the shelter hospital on the track, began to run well, Ling Hong is also slowly recovering.

After that, the bunker hospital kept upping the ante. The National Development and Reform Commission (NDRC) announced on February 16 that it will continue to allocate 230 million yuan of investment from the central budget to support Wuhan's Shelter Hospital in improving its facilities, adding necessary medical equipment and enhancing its admission capacity.

At the same time, a huge amount of medical support from all over the country. As of February 20, a total of 251 medical teams with 32,446 personnel had assisted Wuhan, of which 73 medical teams with 8,220 personnel had assisted the shelter hospital and 178 medical teams with 24,226 personnel had assisted the designated hospital.

The way to solve the problem of beds in Wuhan as a whole is to "two additional and one transformation" —— -- to increase the number of fixed-point hospital and the number of square-shaped hospital, and to transform the centralized isolation point into the isolation treatment point.

On February 21, Hu Yabo, a member of the Standing Committee of the Wuhan Municipal Committee of the Communist Party of China and Executive Vice Mayor, said that in view of the fact that more new patients are still coming in, the Central Guidance Group led provinces and cities to set up a special class of resources and put forward the "3318" working target, that is, until February 25, the target of 30,000 reserved beds for designated hospitals, 30,000 reserved beds for shelter hospitals, 10,000 reserved beds for isolated treatment sites and 80,000 reserved beds for isolated sites has been achieved through collection, expansion and renovation.

These 150,000 beds, hope to keep Wuhan "bed and others" bottom line.

The bottom line

With the gradual realization of "bed and others" , the gradual deepening of the understanding of the virus, and the continuous optimization of treatment programs, the epidemic situation in Wuhan has some positive changes: the number of newly diagnosed cases per day has dropped to 314 on February 21; The number of suspected cases dropped to 927; the number of new discharges rose to 992 on the 21st.

Moreover, on February 20 and 21, the number of newly discharged patients exceeded the number of newly confirmed cases.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
New Cases confirmed and discharged in Wuhan in February

"In general, the epidemic in Hubei and Wuhan has slowed down from the previous explosive growth, and if prevention and control measures are put in place, the downward trend will not change, starting from the previous peak, " Ding said.

However, the turning point has not come, Wuhan's situation is still grim.

From the point of view of prevention and control, Wuhan needs to control the source of infection thoroughly and cut off the route of transmission.

As of February 21, there were 36,680 confirmed cases in Wuhan, including 2,087 critical cases and 7,468 severe cases, accounting for 26% of the total.

"The most important thing at present is to prevent the transformation from mild to severe and from severe to critical, " Ding said.

And to solve this problem, not only should be collected, should be treated, there is a key point, should be as early as possible.

There are three ways to prevent and control epidemic diseases: controlling the source of infection, cutting off the route of transmission and protecting the susceptible population. It is only when each knife is in place that it is possible to control its popularity as quickly as possible.

But after the closure of the city, Wuhan in the three Dao presented a situation of insufficient strength. The only consequence of not being able to find and control the source of infection in the first place is the further spread of the epidemic.

To achieve as early as possible, Wuhan must have an accurate grasp of the basic information of the epidemic situation.

On February 20, Chen Yixin, deputy head of the Central Steering Group and Secretary General of the Central Political and Legal Affairs Commission, arrived at the Wuhan Public Security Bureau's General Command for epidemic prevention and control, the news and Public Opinion Center, and the law enforcement and supervision platform to supervise the epidemic prevention and control work.

To Battle of Wuhan it, he says, one must first understand what it is like to call a "statistical object" -- a person who has been diagnosed, suspected, feverish, or in close contact with others? From the data point of view, how about the trend of prevention and control? Where does the future lie? Must not be "foot on the skin of a watermelon, slide where is where" .

Chen Yixin points out, do a good job of epidemic prevention and control, the bottom is not clear, progress is not clear, will be very passive, even will defeat the war.

Due to the unclear number and progress, the effective experience, including the management of territorialization and classification, did not play an important role in Wuhan for a time.

In order to find out the bottom number, one of the measures taken by Wuhan is to adjust the suspect and diagnostic criteria, so that the source of infection become apparent.

The changes, announced on February 5 in the fifth edition of the COVID-19, include a relaxation of the criteria for suspected cases in Hubei Province, and a change in the classification of cases, "Clinical Diagnosis" was added between "suspected case" and "confirmed case" .

In response, Li Xingwang, a member of the National Medical Expert Group and the chief expert of the Infectious Disease Diagnosis and Research Center of Temple of Earth Hospital in Beijing, said the aim was to find patients early, diagnose them early and treat them in isolation.

The change led to consternation as soon as the February 12 figures were released. On the same day, 13436 new cases (including 12364 clinically diagnosed cases) were reported in Wuhan.

However, from an epidemiological point of view, some public health experts also told the reporter that this figure does not mean the further spread of the epidemic, but rather: The new coronavirus epidemic in Hubei, formally entered the core of prevention and control —— Controlling all the sources of infection and cutting off the route of transmission.

By this time, the city of Wuhan had been closed for 20 days.

But really do this, is the Wuhan epidemic launched a general attack on a fundamental premise.

New Officer on duty

Wuhan figure out the bottom number of the work, still appears to be difficult.

As early as January 24, Wuhan put forward a comprehensive "wartime" state, the implementation of the classification of medical treatment system to ensure that fever patients receive timely treatment.

On February 2, the pneumonia control and Prevention Headquarters of the Wuhan COVID-19 requested that all urban districts complete the centralized admission of confirmed patients and the centralized isolation of suspected patients by 12 o'clock on February 2, can Not rule out the fever patients and close contacts of the confirmed patients concentrated isolation observation, additional personnel "clear moon knot. ".

By presenting goals over and over again, it also means that the last deployment may not have achieved them.

Around February 8th and 9th, Ding said, Wuhan called for a decisive battle and a general offensive. The central guidance team asked Hubei Province and Wuhan to carry out a network of screening, not a door, not a person, the patient to the hospital, Shelter Hospital, timely treatment, close contacts found in isolation observation.

Ma Guoqiang, the Wuhan Party secretary at the time, said that as of February 9, a total of 3,371 community villages had been surveyed, with 4.21 million households and 10.59 million people, according to the number of households. The percentage of households surveyed reached 98.6 percent, and the percentage of people surveyed reached 99 percent. As of noon on February 10,1499 newly diagnosed patients with severe pneumonia have been admitted to hospital, Wuhan will strive to complete all suspected patients by the 11th test clear zero.

This group of data is much questioned, many netizen make fun of oneself just belong to 1% .

At this time, Weibo "difficult hospital" information still has a lot of help. First Business reporter continues to receive requests for help from Ms. Gao, a resident of the Xichangkou community at the foot of Wuchang District Yellow Crane Tower, Wuhan, his Grandmother, Feng Yichun, who said she was 82, was not admitted to the hospital after she was diagnosed with bilateral lung infection on CT on February 8 and tested positive for nucleic acid on February 11.

It wasn't until about 4 p.m. on February 13 that Ms. Gao said by telephone that Feng was finally admitted to a designated hospital in Wuhan.

A number of cases have shown that this round of "due diligence" and screening work, is not done well.

On February 12th it became a new reality -- as if it were at its most difficult.

The strategy of this stage is also very clear: Hubei and Wuhan Epidemic Prevention and control is the top priority, is to win the epidemic prevention and control of the decisive battle.

At this time, Hubei Shuai.

On Feb. 13, Hubei and Wuhan traded horses for Jiang. Ying Yong, a former Mayor of Shanghai, took over as a member, member and secretary of the Hubei Provincial Party Committee, and Wang Zhonglin, the former secretary of the Jinan Municipal Party Committee, took over as a member and secretary of the Hubei Provincial Party Committee and the Standing Committee and the Wuhan Municipal Party Committee.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Ying Yong was transferred to Hubei Provincial Party secretary

Two long-serving officials of the political and legal systems have taken over at the heart of the outbreak.

On February 15, the new Wuhan Party secretary, Wang Zhonglin, at the video dispatch meeting of the new Crown Pneumonia Epidemic Command in Wuhan, pointed out the problems that had been found in some small districts, the investigation attitude is not resolute, the measure is not strict, the Mesh is too big.

Then, "full coverage, pull network-style" once again, Wang Zhonglin said, "we can not wait, drag, slow! "

As requested, the investigation will implement five "100 percent" : 100 percent collection of confirmed patients, 100 percent nucleic acid testing of suspected patients, 100 percent testing of fever patients, 100 percent isolation of close contacts, 100 percent of residential villages to implement 24-hour closed management.

"Do not leak a house, do not drop a person" request again, and February 17 to February 19 within three days must ensure that all the above personnel in place, to achieve clear zero.

ONCE SELF-DEPRECATING FOR 1% of Wuhan people, finally received a community investigation phone, or by the community staff knocked on the door.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On February 18, residents of the Qinghe neighborhood in Qingshan District, Wuhan's workers'village were searched.

On the evening of February 18, first business reporter received a request for help from Ms. Liu, who lives near Xinhua road in Jianghan district. Her father, who is in his 80s, was diagnosed with new crown pneumonia in a welfare home. His life was in danger. The hospital and the community "let's wait. " There has been no news of when he will be admitted to the hospital,"the family was worried.

On Feb. 19, Ms. Liu told reporters that an ambulance had taken her father to a designated hospital. "This time it is really due to collect all, do not miss a person. ".

February 19th is also the week of Ying Yong and Wang. On This Day, the information on the micro-blog platform about the help-seeking of the new pneumonia patients was cleared to zero.
